I&#39;m trying to migrate to use React Router 4 and having some trouble understanding the logic of the `&lt;Switch&gt;` component as it&#39;s used in the [docs](https://reacttraining.com/react-router/web/example/no-match) to handle a 404 (or unmatched) route.

